Key Terms Related to Workload

Database: System for capturing and storing structured data

OLTP: Database optimized for many small transactions

OLAP: Database optimized for analyzing aggregated historical data

Data warehouse: System optimized for retrieving and understanding relationships and trends within data

Data Mart: A subset of data for a department or line of business.

Concurrency: Simultaneous users or queries (causes bottlenecks)

Business Intelligence (BI): Analyzing data to make better business decisions